{"tid":2076824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第41期牆紙】香港民族","createTime":"2020-06-24T00:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T06:13:13.000Z","uid":253119,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd75e4cf5c05c87b0005f6ad2899da9fb62ae75","tid":2076824,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:03:51.000Z","msg":"香港民族，從七一講到如今，還是說不清。定義始終模糊，香港「前殖民地」及一國兩制的背景，更令定義工作複雜；但能肯定的是，香港民族是港獨最強大的理論後盾，也是解釋社會情感的不二進路。今期，牆紙開始〈獨立思潮〉的連載，及後與讀者一同了解香港民族與其特色。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 獨立思潮 1 &mdash; 追本溯源 尋找香港民族<br />\n2. 香港民族：定義同釋疑<br />\n3. 你我情同手足 就係香港民族<br />\n4.「種族歧視」只是中國人的遮羞布<br />\n5. 廣東話捍衞戰<br />\n6. 光輝歲月 香港人香港事 <br />\n7. 香港：作為中國的法律恐怖主義基地<br />\n8. 2020年中國與全球風險<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#41st #41期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSM54uN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSM54uN.jpg&h=1824efc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmNQv9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmNQv9P.jpg&h=89d6b511&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyNha9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyNha9R.jpg&h=03ed0005&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNR2ngx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNR2ngx.jpg&h=51462bda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8XMOWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8XMOWz.jpg&h=06ce44ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZxEpuV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZxEpuV.jpg&h=137374b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1hAHgC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/